thread.title: Bangladesh Blasts Kill One

author: wsjcom
title: Bangladesh Blasts Kill One
text:
DHAKA, Bangladesh—Police say unidentified attackers threw homemade bombs early Saturday at thousands of Shiite Muslims gathered for a traditional procession to a shrine in Bangladesh’s capital, leaving one dead and more than 100 injured.
